      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but shows noticeable wear both inside and out. The exterior has minor dents, scratches, and some surface rust in areas. The interior is worn with visible signs of use including faded upholstery and scuffed trim. No major mechanical issues, but expect some age-related maintenance needs.",
